Paper: hep-th/0204141

Date: 2002-04-17

Title: The thermal energy of a scalar field in a one-dimensional compact space

Authors: E. Elizalde, A. C. Tort

Comments: 13 pages, LaTeX, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D66 (2002) 045033

We discuss some controverted aspects of the evaluation of the thermal energyof a scalar field in a one-dimensional compact space. The calculations arecarried out using a generalised zeta function approach.